V\left(r_{1},r_{2}\right)= & \mathfrak{D}_{e}\left(1-e^{-\beta_{1}\left(r_{1}-r_{1,e}\right)}e^{-\beta_{2}\left(r_{2}-r_{2,e}\right)}\right)^{2}
